title: "SalsaSpectrum: An audit-grade Python library for 21cm HI spectral analysis"
abstract: >-
  A modern, high-performance Python migration of the original MATLAB
  SalsaSpectrum class used by the SALSA radio telescopes. This library
  introduces rigorous physical auditing (Radiometer Equation, Beam Efficiency),
  robust statistical modeling (Colored Noise correction, Hybrid Baselines), and
  a modernized software architecture based on Astropy and SciPy.
